```plantuml
@startuml kineviz-3D-human-pose-tracking_3d-ai-powered-pose-tracking

actor WebcamClient as WC
actor ReceiverClient as RC

participant "Node.js Server" as NJS
participant "TensorFlow Model" as TF
participant "Socket.IO" as SIO
participant "GraphXR" as GX

WC -> NJS : Connect via Socket.IO
NJS -> SIO : Establish connection
WC -> NJS : Send 2D Pose Data
NJS -> TF : Process 2D Pose Data
TF -> NJS : Return Processed 3D Pose
NJS -> SIO : Broadcast 3D Pose Data
SIO -> RC : Send 3D Pose Data
RC -> GX : Visualize 3D Pose

@enduml
```